Description:
IN/SD/WC/090222-1,  312269144 - You have failed to ensure that the 230V ac fixed electrical wiring installation within the welfare block has been constructed and maintained in a condition to prevent, so far as is reasonably practicable, danger.

IN/SD/WC/090222-2,  312269196 - The yard is not organised in such a way that vehicles and pedestrians can circulate in a safe manner, which exposes persons including your employees and persons not in your employment to risks to their health and safety.
